name: ORBITRUNNER - Soundtoy 02
description:
An interactive sound toy developed with Unity in celebration of HEN600K.

Reminted for adaptive resolution feature, UI fix and added support for various mobile devices. Low performance on the first start is due to preloading audio assets for a seamless audio experience later on.

Click on spheres to set notes and speed, the middle cube for the camera. Alternative keyboard controls are listed below. 

Key Up - Speed up
Key Down - Speed down
Key R - Reset speed
Space - Toggle Camera
